title: May To December
description:
Yet another British Comedy Classic, this time it&#039;s Anton Rogers...he plays an english solicitor, who handles a divorce case, and falls in love with a client.

Yes I&#039;m afraid it only in english, although it does have some subs (not sure which).
This is series 1 - disc 2 of 2
I ripped it the usual way, using dvdshrink, with nothing removed.

If it seems i&#039;m uploading a lot, it&#039;s because i want to share as much as i can with my fellow human beings.  I&#039;m only on line until december, so i want to get as many uk classic comedies up as i can.

Have fun...enjoy, and please seed as soon as you can, for as long as you can.
